    <h2>About this Portal</h2>
    <p>The Assignment Portal Project is a comprehensive online platform designed to streamline and enhance the assignment management process for educational institutions, instructors, and students. This project aims to address the challenges faced in traditional assignment submission methods by providing a user-friendly, efficient, and centralized platform for creating, submitting, and managing assignments.
      A responsive website, where students can submit their assignment 
      assigned by faculties.
      also allows faculties to announce new assignments, with an efficient data storage system.</p>
